text: Silvia Iklé (born 12 January 1949) is a Swiss equestrian. She competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from St. Gallen (city)
